Hello IABF Tams! Since extended ang application, now's your chance para humabol. If you have questions or need assistance, please feel free to reach out sa amin ni ate Heart and we'll happily assist you^^

Be sure to check out the IABF SC Publicity and Contents Division if you're interested in:
♡ Conceptiualizing Contents (holidays & events)
♡ Scriptwriting (event & video content)
♡ Voiceovers & hosting video contents
♡ Booth Designing

Interested? Ano pang hinihintay mo? Join us sa PubCon as we soar towards greater heights!✨️

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!
📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

 Join the ITHM MUSIC MAKERS this September 16-17 and be part of something powerful, passionate, and purpose-driven.

SEPTEMBER 15 | MONDAY | 3:00 PM - 5:00 PM
SEPTEMBER 17 | WEDNESDAY | 9:00 AM - 11:00 AM

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdedzbaeqHy8nQeF0UgLFuXLv5ODeD0m2lDRFuiCRyGPRBvlw/viewform?usp=header
